      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-Differential lock. This example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive Vanos service. The chassis remains rigid, supported by a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension setup that provides exceptional feedback. While showing minor signs of use appropriate for its age, the mechanical synchronization and throttle response remain sharp.",
