    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a well-maintained 2018 Lexus RX 350 finished in Nebula Gray Pearl with a Parchment leather interior. This vehicle represents a perfect balance of luxury and utility, showing in honest, reliable condition. The exterior paint retains a high-quality shine, though I want to note a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small, professionally touched-up scuff on the lower rear bumper. The original alloy wheels are in great shape with only very light curb rash on the passenger side. Inside, the cabin is clean and has been kept smoke-free. The leather seats are firm and comfortable, with only slight creasing on the driver's side bolster from regular entry. All electronic components, including the heated seats, sunroof, and infotainment system, are fully operational. Mechanically, this Lexus is sound; it has a complete service history with the most recent oil change and multi-point inspection completed less than 1,000 miles ago. The tires have plenty of life left, and the brakes feel sharp and responsive. This is a dependable, high-quality SUV that has been cared for and is ready for its next owner.",
